2:T71f,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Krisp better than Podcastle?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Krisp scores 8.0 overall while Podcastle scores 7.0. Krisp is best for remote workers on calls and noisy environment meetings, while Podcastle excels for podcast creators and audio content production."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Krisp or Podcastle?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Krisp starts at $8/mo and Podcastle starts at $11.99/mo. Krisp offers a free plan. Podcastle offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Krisp to Podcastle?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Krisp and Podcastle support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Krisp vs Podcastle?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Krisp holds an overall rating of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10. Podcastle has an overall rating of 7/10 and ease of use score of 8/10. Users praise Krisp for best-in-class noise cancellation and Podcastle for all-in-one podcast studio."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Krisp or Podcastle?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Krisp for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Podcastle remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize all-in-one podcast studio. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"P2JZirFppjRTCRUsq6bTg","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","